{"tid":1356542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中年人都開始覺醒了","createTime":"2019-07-23T13:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T14:14:19.000Z","uid":64242,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d565e9c3a07efd882cc96e02b26c8de57bb4870","tid":1356542,"uid":64242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"頭先一路睇何君妖新聞一路咒罵狗官<br />\n家母突然間話 <br />\n其實我地啲中年人最應該出黎<br />\n唔係講出黎行下叫下口號<br />\n而真係唔翻工 幾十萬人坐係街 <br />\n睇下班狗官奈我地咩何<br />\n老一輩就話冇學識者<br />\n我地依輩開始有讀過下書 有經濟能力 <br />\n比起年輕人同老人家 <br />\n我地更加應該出黎罷工對抗政府<br />\n<br />\n平時佢都係出去做下和理非 9嗌下口號<br />\n但頭先聽佢講個翻說話好有連登仔feel<br />\n即刻睇下佢手機 俾我見到家母原來裝咗連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢仲話中年人唔係個個都反暴力 做下冷氣軍師<br />\n而係應該利用自己地位同能力保護香港<br />\n<br />\n一直都好感恩有開明嘅父母 <br />\n如果咁多位覺得氣緩而屋企人又唔支持發夢嘅 <br />\n不妨係依到發洩 你肯講我地肯聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個不能少！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"b3da7f6e244e0fbdce2451f93ee7117b143b67ed","tid":1356542,"uid":64242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"香港人的下一步<br />\n光復元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【上熱門呀】元朗遊行詳細po，推正經po啦，咪再講好多垃圾po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356135</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aefb3d44b38d2d52844a0f01a2238b748165cab4","tid":1356542,"uid":279085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfN